Under the original planning document for the inauguration ceremony, Supreme Court Justice Brett M. Kavanaugh was supposed to be swearing in JD Vance as vice president at 11:32 a.m. Eastern time. The event is running  behind schedule, by perhaps 30 minutes or so.
